This versatile baking set offers best-in-class baking performance with the flexibility to store and transport foods while keeping them fresh. The extra tall sides of the High Sided Half Sheet allow for double and triple batches of brownies, bars and sheet cakes while helping to keep foods contained when preparing savory sheet pan meals or roasting vegetables. It’s ideal as a holiday roasting pan for turkey too. The classic half sheet is a kitchen staple for ingredient prep, baking and serving. A see-through lid is included and fits over the rim of both pans for storage of baked goods. Nordic Ware Naturals® sheet pans are made of pure uncoated aluminum which conducts heat rapidly and evenly for beautifully browned foods no matter what you bake, sweet or savory. Aluminum will never rust, and encapsulated steel rims prevent warping of pans when they are placed into a hot oven. The pans and lid nest together for compact storage. Once you use them, you’ll understand why uncoated natural sheet pans are an indispensable classic in both professional and home kitchens alike. Proudly American-made by Nordic Ware, a family-owned business since 1946.
